{
  "Name": "Haz 8x2 SSCPGE | Scout Stationary Clear Practice Non-SP Scout Edition | B01",
  "Description": "
Designed specifically for grounded Scout solo stationary-clearing practice.

Base Settings:

Based on StoneMason's 8x2.

4-player scaling.

Adjustments:

Reduced the Swarmer cap to 60.

The first resupply is free; subsequent ones cost 60 Nitra.

Increased projectile speed to CN Haz 8 level (2.3).

Massively nerfed resistances for large enemies (excluding stationaries).

Massively reduced spawn counts for all non-stationary enemies.

Massively nerfed Bulk Detonator resistances.

Lowered spawn rates for Stalkers and Stingtails.

Rules:

The goal is simply to clear out the high-threat stationaries—you don't need to actually finish the mission.

You can teleport straight into the main cave and start clearing.

Bosco is allowed. 

Recommended Mods:

Enemy Count (to monitor your clear progress and gauge the room's difficulty).

Custom Mission (so you can manually select the exact mission type you want to practice on).
	",
